## Common questions

**How do I enhance a photo?**
Open Picra, tap **Develop Photo**, pick a photo, choose a look, and tap **Enhance**.

**How many free enhancements do I get?**
Your first enhancement is free. **Picra Premium** unlocks more — see the in-app plans.

**How do I manage or cancel my subscription?**
On your iPhone: **Settings → [your name] → Subscriptions → Picra**. You can cancel anytime; access continues until the end of the current period.

**How do I restore a purchase?**
Open Picra → **Profile → Restore Purchase**.

**Where are my photos stored?**
Enhanced photos are saved on your device (in the app's Gallery, and to your Photos if you choose). See our [Privacy Policy](https://bruno12608.github.io/picra-legal/privacy).

